<font color="yellow">(Witness waiting room)</font>

23
00:01:51,050 --> 00:01:54,510
<font color="yellow">You have to keep your promise.</font>

24
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:55,700
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

25
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:57,900
<font color="yellow">This independent prosecutor...</font>

26
00:01:58,260 --> 00:02:00,560
<font color="yellow">will sentence you as promised.</font>

27
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,700
<font color="yellow">I was talking to Chairman Kang.</font>

28
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,960
<font color="yellow">Tell the truth at the court.</font>

29
00:02:05,530 --> 00:02:07,660
<font color="yellow">I will give you enough money for your family...</font>

30
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:09,600
<font color="yellow">to live comfortably in the US.</font>

31
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:12,860
<font color="yellow">You all are like Il Jae.</font>

32
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:15,500
<font color="yellow">You pretended to be just,</font>

