00:02:16,330 --> 00:02:18,100
<font color="yellow">but you've also bribed me like him.</font>

34
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,900
<font color="yellow">If so, you can just tell the truth without the money.</font>

35
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:24,670
<font color="yellow">Do you know what I was relieved about?</font>

36
00:02:26,330 --> 00:02:28,830
<font color="yellow">The fact that I can reveal the truth at the stake of money.</font>

37
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:32,460
<font color="yellow">This is how I narrowly gather and wisely spend.</font>

38
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:35,880
<font color="yellow">Stop it, Chairman Kang.</font>

39
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:38,900
<font color="yellow">Our witness must be nervous.</font>

40
00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:52,930
<font color="yellow">Is the result out for the content of the syringe?</font>

41
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:57,050
<font color="yellow">- Not yet.
