<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

45
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:06,360
<font color="yellow">- Pardon?
-  You look rather anxious.</font>

46
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:09,560
<font color="yellow">I'll be fine soon.</font>

47
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:12,230
<font color="yellow">I need some fresh air.</font>

48
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:13,230
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

49
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,630
<font color="yellow">She's never been like this.</font>

50
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:23,460
<font color="yellow">She must be nervous because she's fighting against Il Jae.</font>

51
00:03:27,330 --> 00:03:28,600
<font color="yellow">It's me, Soo Tak.</font>

52
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:31,260
<font color="yellow">Can you get some Xanax?</font>

53
00:04:14,930 --> 00:04:16,130
