<font color="yellow">I'll make this short.</font>

55
00:04:19,530 --> 00:04:21,320
<font color="yellow">I don't want to speak with you.</font>

56
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,530
<font color="yellow">If you hang up,</font>

57
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:26,700
<font color="yellow">you'll regret what will happen afterwards for life.</font>

58
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,800
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

59
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,830
<font color="yellow">Shortly,</font>

60
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:33,800
<font color="yellow">you will receive a phone call from the US.</font>

61
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,860
<font color="yellow">You'll find out...</font>

62
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:38,530
<font color="yellow">what I'm talking about...</font>

63
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:40,260
<font color="yellow">after that phone call.</font>

64
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:10,730
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

65
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,600
<font color="yellow">You're working so hard.</font>

66
00:05:15,930 --> 00:05:18,400
<font color="yellow">I can't make any mistakes in front of Il Jae,</font>

67
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,230
<font color="yellow">but I keep forgetting my questions.</font>

68
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,970
<font color="yellow">Give it to me. I haven't got time.</font>

69
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:27,100
<font color="yellow">You've prepared more than enough for this.</font>

70
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,200
<font color="yellow">I thought I did, but I don't think it was enough.</font>

71
00:05:30,730 --> 00:05:32,630
<font color="yellow">He needs to be proven guilty in this trial.</font>

72
00:05:34,430 --> 00:05:35,660
<font color="yellow">Look at my eyes for a second.</font>

73
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,860
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo, the trial will be...</font>

74
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:41,330
<font color="yellow">Calm down and look at me, Soo Yeon.</font>

75
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,880
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

76
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,400
<font color="yellow">Do you remember...</font>

77
00:05:56,530 --> 00:06:00,500
<font color="yellow">how I asked you to put on my tie when you were my assistant?</font>

78
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:25,460
<font color="yellow">With the presentation coming along,</font>

79
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:27,060
<font color="yellow">I was really nervous back then.</font>

80
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,430
<font color="yellow">But when you put that tie on me, I felt more relaxed...</font>

81
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,630
<font color="yellow">and gained courage.</font>

82
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:37,360
<font color="yellow">You'll do great today.</font>

83
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,860
<font color="yellow">I guarantee it.</font>

84
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,630
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Gun Woo.</font>

85
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:55,160
<font color="yellow">Should I give her the Xanax myself?</font>

86
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,600
<font color="yellow">I think that would be better.</font>

87
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,330
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Nam, you can go ahead first.</font>

88
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,360
<font color="yellow">- You should go in.
-  Okay.</font>

89
00:07:26,460 --> 00:07:27,800
<font color="yellow">I believe...</font>

90
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,760
<font color="yellow">I gave you enough chances so far.</font>

91
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:34,060
<font color="yellow">I turned a blind eye to things...</font>

92
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:37,330
<font color="yellow">while hoping for you to come back to your place.</font>

93
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:42,530
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo. You'll realise how foolish...</font>

94
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:43,870
<font color="yellow">your decision was today.</font>

95
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,100
<font color="yellow">I'm fine with that.</font>

96
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:49,740
<font color="yellow">I don't care if I make mistakes or even break and tear.</font>

97
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:50,900
<font color="yellow">At least that way,</font>

98
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:53,000
<font color="yellow">I won't become a monster like you.</font>

99
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:55,300
<font color="yellow">A monster?</font>

100
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:59,530
<font color="yellow">The real monster is the world, not the person.</font>

101
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:03,960
<font color="yellow">Once Dodo Group goes under Gwi Ja and Gwang Woo's power,</font>

102
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:08,130
<font color="yellow">you'll see what a monster really looks like.</font>

103
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,330
<font color="yellow">Did you see that?</font>

104
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:18,630
<font color="yellow">Look at that. If his eyes could kill,</font>

105
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:21,560
<font color="yellow">he would have killed Gun Woo already.</font>

106
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,730
<font color="yellow">You're right. By the way,</font>

107
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:26,900
<font color="yellow">which side should we be cheering for?</font>

108
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,160
<font color="yellow">Since it came to this,</font>

109
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,900
<font color="yellow">it'd be better for Il Jae to be convicted.</font>

110
00:08:32,830 --> 00:08:35,260
<font color="yellow">That's true. If Il Jae is found guilty,</font>

111
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:38,760
<font color="yellow">the two of them will never work together again.</font>

112
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:40,760
<font color="yellow">That, too.</font>

113
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,530
<font color="yellow">But Soo Yeon is their prosecutor.</font>

114
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:47,300
<font color="yellow">We should support her fully.</font>

115
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:50,600
<font color="yellow">In any case, all we have to do...</font>

116
00:08:51,330 --> 00:08:54,130
<font color="yellow">is sit back and watch.</font>

117
00:08:56,130 --> 00:08:57,300
<font color="yellow">Let's enjoy this.</font>

118
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:01,930
<font color="yellow">Case number 4958.</font>

119
00:09:01,930 --> 00:09:05,000
<font color="yellow">We'll start the hearing on the violation of the election law...</font>

120
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,360
<font color="yellow">by the Seoul mayor.</font>

121
00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:09,460
<font color="yellow">Prosecution. You may interrogate the undertrial.</font>

122
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,330
<font color="yellow">During the Seoul mayoral campaign,</font>

123
00:09:27,330 --> 00:09:29,950
<font color="yellow">you've handed over money to an independent candidate,</font>

124
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:33,050
<font color="yellow">Cho Cham, to come to an illegal agreement. Do you admit to this?</font>

125
00:09:33,050 --> 00:09:34,880
<font color="yellow">I never had an illegal agreement.</font>

126
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:38,020
<font color="yellow">Cho has already confessed this to the prosecution.</font>

127
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:39,070
<font color="yellow">It's a conspiracy.</font>

128
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:44,360
<font color="yellow">2.5 million dollars of bearer bond was found in Cho's secret safe.</font>

129
00:09:44,730 --> 00:09:46,830
<font color="yellow">Wasn't it given to him in exchange for giving up his candidacy?</font>

130
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:50,640
<font color="yellow">He was moved by my campaign...</font>

131
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,180
<font color="yellow">and decided to support me.</font>

132
00:09:52,180 --> 00:09:53,730
<font color="yellow">All I did was accept his offer.</font>

133
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:56,630
<font color="yellow">You can meet with my aide, who was with me...</font>

134
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:59,130
<font color="yellow">when I met with Cho,</font>

135
00:09:59,130 --> 00:10:00,600
<font color="yellow">to see if I'm lying or not.</font>

136
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:03,720
<font color="yellow">Defendant, we're at court.</font>

137
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:06,070
<font color="yellow">- If you give false testimony...
-  Prosecutor Oh.</font>

138
00:10:06,570 --> 00:10:10,300
<font color="yellow">Do you still believe that I'm involved in your brother's death?</font>

139
00:10:20,130 --> 00:10:21,130
<font color="yellow">Defendant.</font>

140
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:23,760
<font color="yellow">It's the prosecutor that asks the questions.</font>

141
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,960
<font color="yellow">Are you unfairly targeting me...</font>

142
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,300
<font color="yellow">based on personal feelings?</font>

143
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:30,960
<font color="yellow">I said, I'm the one that will ask questions.</font>

144
00:10:32,130 --> 00:10:34,430
<font color="yellow">Prosecutor Oh, please calm down.</font>

145
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,200
<font color="yellow">Defendant,</font>

146
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,700
<font color="yellow">please do not bring up issues irrelevant to this case.</font>

147
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,960
<font color="yellow">It's related to this case.</font>

148
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,500
<font color="yellow">Candidate Cho...</font>

149
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:47,460
<font color="yellow">might have been asked to do this by someone else's request.</font>

150
00:10:49,430 --> 00:10:50,460
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

151
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:52,340
<font color="yellow">the prosecutor...</font>

152
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:55,660
<font color="yellow">never considered the possibility and ruled it out from the start.</font>

153
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,100
<font color="yellow">Your Honour.</font>

154
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:04,260
<font color="yellow">I would like to call Cho Cham as a witness.</font>

155
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:18,200
<font color="yellow">Il Jae is putting up a good fight.</font>

156
00:11:18,730 --> 00:11:19,730
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

157
00:11:21,230 --> 00:11:22,700
<font color="yellow">doesn't Soo Yeon look so cool?</font>

158
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,360
<font color="yellow">(Witness)</font>

159
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:40,400
<font color="yellow">I think the game is over now.</font>

160
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,000
<font color="yellow">You have received 2.5 million dollars' worth...</font>

161
00:11:46,730 --> 00:11:48,600
<font color="yellow">of bearer bonds for supporting...</font>

162
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:51,700
<font color="yellow">Byun Il Jae during the Seoul mayoral election.</font>

163
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:53,260
<font color="yellow">Is this true?</font>

164
00:11:57,700 --> 00:11:59,730
<font color="yellow">Please answer my question.</font>

165
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,960
<font color="yellow">Witness.</font>

166
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:06,700
<font color="yellow">That...</font>

167
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,460
<font color="yellow">never happened.</font>

168
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:24,700
<font color="yellow">You already confessed during the interrogation.</font>

169
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:25,730
<font color="yellow">I was forced...</font>

170
00:12:28,060 --> 00:12:30,060
<font color="yellow">to confess a lie.</font>

171
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,330
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

172
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:42,530
<font color="yellow">Are you being threatened by him?</font>

173
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:47,760
<font color="yellow">Shortly, you will receive a phone call from the US.</font>

174
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,460
<font color="yellow">Honey. Eun Sol, it's Dad.</font>

175
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:57,500
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

176
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:01,200
<font color="yellow">Honey, today's the trial. Right?</font>

177
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:03,160
<font color="yellow">I didn't go because you told me not to...</font>

178
00:13:03,930 --> 00:13:05,860
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about your wife and your daughter.</font>

179
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,530
<font color="yellow">I'll give them a tour.</font>

180
00:13:09,430 --> 00:13:10,600
<font color="yellow">Eun Sol, say bye to your dad.</font>

181
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:12,200
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

182
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:15,500
<font color="yellow">You... Why are you there?</font>

183
00:13:21,130 --> 00:13:25,000
<font color="yellow">The number is currently turned off. Please leave a message after...</font>

184
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,030
<font color="yellow">Did you say her name was Eun Sol?</font>

185
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:39,700
<font color="yellow">You have a beautiful daughter.</font>

186
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,200
<font color="yellow">Hey...</font>

187
00:13:41,830 --> 00:13:42,860
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing?</font>

188
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,830
<font color="yellow">How I'll act...</font>

189
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:47,000
<font color="yellow">depends on you.</font>

190
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:51,230
<font color="yellow">I'm sure you already know what you have to do at court...</font>

191
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,960
<font color="yellow">without my explaining it.</font>

192
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,900
<font color="yellow">Look here, Byun Il Jae!</font>

193
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:58,300
<font color="yellow">The man who's currently with your family...</font>

194
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,560
<font color="yellow">tends to get very violent at times.</font>

195
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,860
<font color="yellow">I'll see you in court, Mr Cho.</font>

196
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:27,330
<font color="yellow">Your Honour. There was an incident this morning...</font>

197
00:14:27,330 --> 00:14:29,960
<font color="yellow">at the detention centre where our witness almost lost his life.</font>

198
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:34,360
<font color="yellow">We have suspicions that the defendant instigated the attack.</font>

199
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:35,930
<font color="yellow">I object.</font>

200
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:40,580
<font color="yellow">The prosecution is defaming the defendant without any evidence.</font>

201
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:45,000
<font color="yellow">We will find out in this very court if I'm defaming him or not.</font>

202
00:14:55,330 --> 00:14:56,580
<font color="yellow">Witness.</font>

203
00:14:56,580 --> 00:14:58,800
<font color="yellow">Have you ever felt that your life was in danger?</font>

204
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:01,830
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

205
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:15,080
<font color="yellow">Someone attempted to murder him with poison in a syringe.</font>

206
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:17,600
<font color="yellow">The syringe you're talking about is...</font>

207
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:21,900
<font color="yellow">the insulin I take for my diabetes.</font>

208
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,400
<font color="yellow">Something seems off.</font>

209
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:35,300
<font color="yellow">I have a bad feeling about this.</font>

210
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:44,900
<font color="yellow">The result from the chemical test to find the components...</font>

211
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,330
<font color="yellow">of that syringe has arrived.</font>

212
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:04,960
<font color="yellow">Prosecutor. What was in the syringe that almost killed the witness?</font>

213
