00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:18,700
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

486
00:34:19,830 --> 00:34:21,030
<font color="yellow">Do you know...</font>

487
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,060
<font color="yellow">how I feel these days?</font>

488
00:34:23,930 --> 00:34:27,430
<font color="yellow">I'm reminded of you whenever I'm eating something delicious.</font>

489
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,700
<font color="yellow">I'm reminded of you whenever I see anything beautiful.</font>

490
00:34:32,930 --> 00:34:36,700
<font color="yellow">I'm reminded of you whenever there is something fun happening.</font>

491
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:38,430
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

492
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:41,430
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon. Oh Soo Yeon!</font>

493
00:34:44,200 --> 00:34:47,300
<font color="yellow">All I can think about is you.</font>

494
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,630
<font color="yellow">If Il Jae...</font>

495
00:34:52,100 --> 00:34:54,000
<font color="yellow">wins this trial,</font>

496
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:56,830
<font color="yellow">he'll give you a really hard time.</font>

497
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:02,360
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo has been abandoned by Il Jae and is useless now.</font>

498
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,670
<font color="yellow">You should think realistically.</font>

499
00:35:06,930 --> 00:35:10,060
<font color="yellow">I'm the only one who can protect you.</font>

500
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:12,230
<font color="yellow">You should go see a psychiatrist.</font>

