502
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,830
<font color="yellow">Hey, watch it.</font>

503
00:35:19,830 --> 00:35:21,170
<font color="yellow">Get treatment.</font>

504
00:35:21,170 --> 00:35:24,700
<font color="yellow">I hope you'll realise why I despise you so much.</font>

505
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,460
<font color="yellow">How could you?</font>

506
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:30,850
<font color="yellow">I barely controlled myself from going astray...</font>

507
00:35:30,850 --> 00:35:32,830
<font color="yellow">and came here.</font>

508
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:35,030
<font color="yellow">I don't care what happens to you.</font>

509
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:36,060
<font color="yellow">Get lost.</font>

510
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,700
<font color="yellow">Why are you...</font>

511
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:40,980
<font color="yellow">saying the same thing as my father did?</font>

512
00:35:40,980 --> 00:35:42,510
<font color="yellow">I said, get lost.</font>

513
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:44,300
<font color="yellow">Otherwise, I'll report you for trespassing.</font>

514
00:36:00,130 --> 00:36:02,700
<font color="yellow">I guess you still don't realise...</font>

515
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,200
<font color="yellow">how much of a scary person I am.</font>

516
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,880
<font color="yellow">What do you think?</font>

517
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:16,300
<font color="yellow">Is it good enough for the Chinese shipowners?</font>

518
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:17,700
<font color="yellow">Well done.</font>

