537
00:37:22,300 --> 00:37:23,300
<font color="yellow">Nothing.</font>

538
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:25,830
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

539
00:37:26,330 --> 00:37:28,260
<font color="yellow">I wanted to have dinner with him.</font>

