00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:32,560
<font color="yellow">Cho Cham wants a new lawyer.</font>

541
00:37:33,030 --> 00:37:34,860
<font color="yellow">I don't think we can persuade him.</font>

542
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:36,850
<font color="yellow">Where is Chae Ryung?</font>

543
00:37:36,850 --> 00:37:38,730
