00:37:43,850 --> 00:37:47,170
<font color="yellow">and the other has been turned off for days.</font>

547
00:37:47,170 --> 00:37:50,330
<font color="yellow">We can't locate it unless it's turned on.</font>

548
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:53,680
<font color="yellow">This is bad. The second trial's nearing.</font>

