00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,800
<font color="yellow">Don't.</font>

558
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:19,930
<font color="yellow">However bad things turn out, we must stick to the books.</font>

559
00:38:19,930 --> 00:38:21,670
