00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,730
<font color="yellow">Untying yourself...</font>

567
00:39:13,200 --> 00:39:14,670
<font color="yellow">won't get you anywhere.</font>

568
00:39:27,060 --> 00:39:28,930
<font color="yellow">Your lips are chapped.</font>

