00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:38,300
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

570
00:39:40,170 --> 00:39:42,960
<font color="yellow">You must be very thirsty.</font>

571
00:39:44,230 --> 00:39:45,830
<font color="yellow">I don't need your pity.</font>

572
00:39:47,170 --> 00:39:48,630
<font color="yellow">The trial concludes tomorrow.</font>

573
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:52,360
