00:40:10,330 --> 00:40:12,500
<font color="yellow">If I didn't find out that you were a spy,</font>

577
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,860
<font color="yellow">I'd have sold my soul for you.</font>

578
00:40:18,200 --> 00:40:20,030
<font color="yellow">Of all the women I've met,</font>

579
00:40:20,030 --> 00:40:21,700
<font color="yellow">you're the most charming...</font>

580
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:27,400
<font color="yellow">Of all the men I've met...</font>

581
00:40:28,170 --> 00:40:30,060
<font color="yellow">you are the worst.</font>

582
00:40:45,200 --> 00:40:47,400
<font color="yellow">I love your fiery personality.</font>

583
00:40:49,030 --> 00:40:50,700
<font color="yellow">It's such a pity to think...</font>

584
00:40:51,170 --> 00:40:52,200
<font color="yellow">it'll die with you.</font>

585
00:41:09,130 --> 00:41:10,500
<font color="yellow">Sir, Sir.</font>

