00:41:36,530 --> 00:41:37,630
<font color="yellow">He's your son.</font>

594
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:41,530
<font color="yellow">He's the son we made together.</font>

595
00:41:43,200 --> 00:41:44,500
<font color="yellow">Don't you feel sorry for him?</font>

596
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:46,000
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo...</font>

597
00:41:46,930 --> 00:41:48,200
<font color="yellow">is your son.</font>

598
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:50,430
<font color="yellow">He isn't mine.</font>

599
00:41:51,100 --> 00:41:52,100
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

600
00:41:52,430 --> 00:41:54,800
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo is my only son.</font>

601
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:58,030
<font color="yellow">The woman whom I loved...</font>

602
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:03,000
