603
00:42:05,060 --> 00:42:06,460
<font color="yellow">I'm the chairwoman!</font>

604
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:08,500
<font color="yellow">Don't call me Mrs Hwang!</font>

605
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:16,260
<font color="yellow">All these years,</font>

606
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:20,300
<font color="yellow">you've hurt me and I bore it through gritted teeth.</font>

607
00:42:22,170 --> 00:42:23,170
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

608
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,300
<font color="yellow">I will not let you...</font>

609
00:42:26,100 --> 00:42:27,760
<font color="yellow">bully my son.</font>

610
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,860
<font color="yellow">Remember that if you want to die an old man.</font>

611
00:42:39,930 --> 00:42:41,330
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

