00:42:41,330 --> 00:42:42,800
<font color="yellow">No, Sir. Calm down.</font>

613
00:42:44,130 --> 00:42:46,700
<font color="yellow">You must hold back. Relax.</font>

614
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:53,260
<font color="yellow">That didn't hurt at all.</font>

615
00:42:54,760 --> 00:42:55,760
<font color="yellow">Right here.</font>

616
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:57,500
<font color="yellow">My heart.</font>

617
00:42:59,230 --> 00:43:00,470
<font color="yellow">It hurts.</font>

618
00:43:00,470 --> 00:43:02,530
<font color="yellow">I'll get you some cold water.</font>

619
00:43:11,860 --> 00:43:12,860
<font color="yellow">Now,</font>

620
00:43:14,860 --> 00:43:15,900
<font color="yellow">I even...</font>

621
00:43:18,230 --> 00:43:20,900
<font color="yellow">get slapped by my own wife.</font>

622
00:43:43,500 --> 00:43:44,500
<font color="yellow">Mr Han's here.</font>

623
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:49,460
<font color="yellow">Why did you want to see me, Sir?</font>

624
00:43:50,130 --> 00:43:51,160
<font color="yellow">I don't care...</font>

625
00:43:51,500 --> 00:43:55,300
<font color="yellow">who you're loyal to or how you rise above others.</font>

626
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,330
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

627
00:43:57,600 --> 00:44:01,390
<font color="yellow">your corrupt way of life threatened my father's life.</font>

628
00:44:01,390 --> 00:44:03,200
<font color="yellow">That, I cannot forgive.</font>

629
00:44:03,700 --> 00:44:05,360
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

630
00:44:06,060 --> 00:44:09,300
<font color="yellow">I have no idea what you mean.</font>

631
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:11,100
<font color="yellow">His medicine.</font>

632
00:44:11,700 --> 00:44:12,700
<font color="yellow">Sorry?</font>

633
00:44:13,600 --> 00:44:15,360
<font color="yellow">The ones who swapped his medicines...</font>

634
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:17,700
<font color="yellow">were you and Chairwoman Hwang.</font>

635
00:44:27,960 --> 00:44:31,560
<font color="yellow">In this is a video that shows what you did.</font>

636
00:44:34,030 --> 00:44:35,160
<font color="yellow">Please forgive me.</font>

637
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:38,400
<font color="yellow">I only did what I was told.</font>

638
00:44:39,030 --> 00:44:41,950
<font color="yellow">No excuse can save you now.</font>

639
00:44:41,950 --> 00:44:43,530
<font color="yellow">It's attempted murder.</font>

640
00:44:43,530 --> 00:44:46,830
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry. Please forgive me this once.</font>

